trans-unit.source: Provides version information for a physical file on disk.
trans-unit.target: Gir versjonsinformasjon for en fysisk fil på disken.

trans-unit.source: Typically, a version number is displayed as "major number.minor number.build number.private part number".
trans-unit.target: Vanligvis vises et versjonsnummer som "hoved number.minor number.build number.private part number".

trans-unit.source: A file version number is a 64-bit number that holds the version number for a file as follows: - The first 16 bits are the <xref:System.Diagnostics.FileVersionInfo.FileMajorPart%2A> number.
trans-unit.target: Et versjonsnummer er et 64-biters nummer som inneholder versjonsnummeret for en fil som følger:-første 16 biter er den <xref:System.Diagnostics.FileVersionInfo.FileMajorPart%2A>tall.</xref:System.Diagnostics.FileVersionInfo.FileMajorPart%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The next 16 bits are the <xref:System.Diagnostics.FileVersionInfo.FileMinorPart%2A> number.
trans-unit.target: -Neste 16 biter er den <xref:System.Diagnostics.FileVersionInfo.FileMinorPart%2A>tall.</xref:System.Diagnostics.FileVersionInfo.FileMinorPart%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The third set of 16 bits are the <xref:System.Diagnostics.FileVersionInfo.FileBuildPart%2A> number.
trans-unit.target: -Det tredje settet 16-biters er den <xref:System.Diagnostics.FileVersionInfo.FileBuildPart%2A>tall.</xref:System.Diagnostics.FileVersionInfo.FileBuildPart%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The last 16 bits are the <xref:System.Diagnostics.FileVersionInfo.FilePrivatePart%2A> number.
trans-unit.target: -Siste 16 biter er den <xref:System.Diagnostics.FileVersionInfo.FilePrivatePart%2A>tall.</xref:System.Diagnostics.FileVersionInfo.FilePrivatePart%2A>

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Diagnostics.FileVersionInfo.GetVersionInfo%2A> method of this class to get a FileVersionInfo containing information about a file, then look at the properties for information about the file.
trans-unit.target: Bruk av <xref:System.Diagnostics.FileVersionInfo.GetVersionInfo%2A>-metoden til denne klassen for å få en FileVersionInfo som inneholder informasjon om en fil, deretter se egenskapene for informasjon om filen.</xref:System.Diagnostics.FileVersionInfo.GetVersionInfo%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Diagnostics.FileVersionInfo.FileVersion%2A> property provides version information about the file.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Diagnostics.FileVersionInfo.FileVersion%2A>egenskapen gir versjonsinformasjon om filen.</xref:System.Diagnostics.FileVersionInfo.FileVersion%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Diagnostics.FileVersionInfo.ProductMajorPart%2A>, <xref:System.Diagnostics.FileVersionInfo.ProductMinorPart%2A>, <xref:System.Diagnostics.FileVersionInfo.ProductBuildPart%2A>, <xref:System.Diagnostics.FileVersionInfo.ProductPrivatePart%2A>, and <xref:System.Diagnostics.FileVersionInfo.ProductVersion%2A> properties provide version information for the product that the specified file is a part of.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Diagnostics.FileVersionInfo.ProductMajorPart%2A>, <xref:System.Diagnostics.FileVersionInfo.ProductMinorPart%2A>, <xref:System.Diagnostics.FileVersionInfo.ProductBuildPart%2A>, <xref:System.Diagnostics.FileVersionInfo.ProductPrivatePart%2A>, og <xref:System.Diagnostics.FileVersionInfo.ProductVersion%2A>Egenskaper inneholder versjonsinformasjon for den angitte filen er en del av produktet.</xref:System.Diagnostics.FileVersionInfo.ProductVersion%2A> </xref:System.Diagnostics.FileVersionInfo.ProductPrivatePart%2A> </xref:System.Diagnostics.FileVersionInfo.ProductBuildPart%2A> </xref:System.Diagnostics.FileVersionInfo.ProductMinorPart%2A> </xref:System.Diagnostics.FileVersionInfo.ProductMajorPart%2A>

trans-unit.source: Call <xref:System.Diagnostics.FileVersionInfo.ToString%2A> to get a partial list of properties and their values for this file.
trans-unit.target: Kall <xref:System.Diagnostics.FileVersionInfo.ToString%2A>å hente en delvis liste over egenskapene og verdiene for denne filen.</xref:System.Diagnostics.FileVersionInfo.ToString%2A>

trans-unit.source: The FileVersionInfo properties are based on version resource information built into the file.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapene FileVersionInfo er basert på ressursen for versjonsinformasjon bygget inn i filen.

trans-unit.source: Version resources are often built into binary files such as .exe or .dll files; text files do not have version resource information.
trans-unit.target: Versjonsressurser er ofte innebygd i binærfiler for eksempel .exe eller DLL-filer. tekstfiler har ikke versjonsinformasjon for ressursen.

trans-unit.source: Version resources are typically specified in a Win32 resource file, or in assembly attributes.
trans-unit.target: Versjonsressurser er vanligvis angitt i en Win32-ressursfil eller i samlingen attributter.

trans-unit.source: For example the <xref:System.Diagnostics.FileVersionInfo.IsDebug%2A> property reflects the `VS_FF_DEBUG` flag value in the file's `VS_FIXEDFILEINFO` block, which is built from the `VERSIONINFO` resource in a Win32 resource file.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel den <xref:System.Diagnostics.FileVersionInfo.IsDebug%2A>egenskapen gjenspeiler de `VS_FF_DEBUG` flagget verdien i filen `VS_FIXEDFILEINFO` blokk, noe som er bygd fra den `VERSIONINFO` ressurser i en Win32-ressursfil.</xref:System.Diagnostics.FileVersionInfo.IsDebug%2A>

trans-unit.source: For more information about specifying version resources in a Win32 resource file, see "About Resource Files" and "VERSIONINFO Resource" in the Platform SDK.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon om hvordan du angir versjonsressurser i en Win32-ressursfil, kan du se "Om ressursfiler" og "VERSIONINFO ressurs" i SDK.

trans-unit.source: For more information about specifying version resources in a .NET module, see the [Setting Assembly Attributes](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) topic.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon om hvordan du angir versjonsressurser i en .NET-modul, kan du se den [innstillingen samlingen attributter](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) emnet.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > This class makes a link demand at the class level that applies to all members.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Denne klassen er en kobling behov på klassen nivået som gjelder for alle medlemmer.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Security.SecurityException> is thrown when the immediate caller does not have full trust permission.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Security.SecurityException>forårsakes når umiddelbar oppkalleren ikke har tillatelse for fullstendig klarering.</xref:System.Security.SecurityException>

trans-unit.source: For details about link demands, see [Link Demands](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: For mer informasjon om krav til koblingen, kan du se [koblingen krav](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
